VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:Preferences\.Set|Application\.Current\.Properties\[)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:Preferences\.Set.*(?:password|token|secret|key|auth|credential)|Application\.Current\.Properties\[.*(?:password|token|secret|key|auth|credential)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects local persistence patterns where sensitive value handling should be verified.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Insecure Local Storage of Secrets.
